long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Bullet Force is an exhilarating first-person shooter game that offers players intense multiplayer action and a variety of engaging modes, making it a favorite among fans of the genre. The game starts with a choice of modes, including Team Deathmatch, Conquest, Free-For-All, and Gun Game, each offering a unique twist on the FPS formula. 

The heart of Bullet Force lies in its customization options. Players can choose from over 20 weapons, ranging from assault rifles to snipers, each of which can be outfitted with multiple attachments like scopes, extended magazines, and laser sights. This level of customization allows players to tailor their loadouts to suit their play style and the tactical needs of different maps and modes.

4. Press "Remove"
